    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>YOU ARE GLIP.</i><br><br><br><i>THE INSIDE OF THESE WALLS IS ALL YOU HAVE EVER KNOWN.</i><br><br><br><i>IT IS TIME TO BE FREE.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soul Nexus is a text-based adventure game where you explore strange environments and encounter even stranger individuals. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/b39654fcd4712c8e010ef4e3d7ce8349.poster.avif?t=1749485965\" width=620 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/b39654fcd4712c8e010ef4e3d7ce8349.webm?t=1749485965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/b39654fcd4712c8e010ef4e3d7ce8349.mp4?t=1749485965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore over 150 different rooms and locations over the course of 4 acts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles, find secrets, jump in mysterious holes, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/a9f71209b62f50a6cb6f41cb6d2d1f34.poster.avif?t=1749485965\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/a9f71209b62f50a6cb6f41cb6d2d1f34.webm?t=1749485965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With too many commands for us to bother counting for this description, there's a bunch of stuff you can do!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/4a48ded717e5f976db4e2b04670c2797.poster.avif?t=1749485965\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/4a48ded717e5f976db4e2b04670c2797.webm?t=1749485965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301290/extras/4a48ded717e5f976db4e2b04670c2797.mp4?t=1749485965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
